text.li1: This is a list item in an unordered list
text.li2: An unordered list is a list in which the sequence of items is not important. Sometimes, an unordered list is a bulleted list. And this is a long list item in an unordered list that can wrap onto a new line.
text.li3: Lists can be nested inside of each other
text.li4: This is a nested list item
text.li5: This is another nested list item in an unordered list
text.li6: This is the last list item
